- cs.DB (Databases) is also likely as the paper discusses the efficiency of the new data structure in detecting duplicates in streaming data. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possibility as the paper briefly discusses the effect of adversarial inputs for hash-based duplicate filters. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possibility as duplicate detection is a common problem in information retrieval. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possibility as the paper involves a thorough analysis of algorithms and data structures.
